---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Responsible Disclosure | ByteLite LLC"
  description="Responsible disclosure policy for ByteLite LLC. How to report security vulnerabilities in our website or services."
  noindex={true}
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Security</p>
      <h1>Responsible Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="legal-sub">Last updated: May 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container legal-body">

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>ByteLite LLC takes the security of its website and services seriously. If you believe you have found a security vulnerability, we encourage responsible disclosure.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Scope</h2>
        <p>This policy applies to security issues affecting:</p>
        <ul class="legal-list">
          <li>ByteLite LLC public websites (thebytelite.com)</li>
          <li>Public contact forms and explicitly public services</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Private beta software, research systems, and non-public infrastructure are outside public testing scope unless explicitly authorized in writing by ByteLite LLC.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>How to Report</h2>
        <p>If you have found a security vulnerability, please contact us through the <a href="/contact">contact page</a> or email:</p>
        <p style="margin-top:1rem;"><a href="mailto:security@thebytelite.com" style="color:#818cf8;font-family:monospace;">security@thebytelite.com</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>What to Include</h2>
        <ul class="legal-list">
          <li>Description of the vulnerability</li>
          <li>Steps to reproduce the issue</li>
          <li>Potential impact</li>
          <li>Your contact information</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
        <ul class="legal-list">
          <li>We will acknowledge receipt within 48 hours</li>
          <li>We will provide an initial assessment within 7 days</li>
          <li>We will keep you informed of progress</li>
          <li>We will credit you (if desired) when the issue is resolved</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Please Do Not</h2>
        <ul class="legal-list">
          <li>Access or modify data without permission</li>
          <li>Perform actions that could harm our services or users</li>
          <li>Publicly disclose the issue before we have addressed it</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Legal Protection</h2>
        <p>ByteLite LLC will not pursue legal action against researchers who follow this responsible disclosure policy, act in good faith, and do not cause harm.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>

<style>

.legal-hero { padding: 5rem 0 3.5rem; }
.legal-hero h1 { max-width: 480px; }
.legal-sub { margin-top: .75rem; font-size: .9375rem; color: #555e7a; }
.legal-body { max-width: 760px; }
.legal-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
.legal-section h2 { font-size: 1.375rem; color: #e4e7f2; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-bottom: .75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a2235; }
.legal-section p { font-size: .9375rem; color: #7b829e; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: .875rem; }
.legal-section a { color: #818cf8; }
.legal-section a:hover { color: #a5b4fc; }
.legal-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .625rem; }
.legal-list li { font-size: .9375rem; color: #7b829e; padding-left: 1.25rem; position: relative; line-height: 1.6; }
.legal-list li::before { content: "—"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #4a5068; }

</style>
